#### **题目**：主从复制
1. 复制的基本原理
	- master-> binary log(二进制事件)
	- slave copy binary log from master to relay log
	- slave redo binary log
2. 基本原则
    - slave(多个) - master(一个）
    - slave only have one server ID
3. 配置
	- server id
	- bin log
	- master 授权 -> show master status -> slave 配置master, start slaver-> show slaver status
	
